{"arkId":"cl010449186","url":"https:\/\/collections.louvre.fr\/ark:\/53355\/cl010449186","modified ":"2026-03-07","title":"De Vermeer \u00e0 V\u00e9ron\u00e8se","titleComplement":"","denominationTitle":[{"type":"D\u00e9nomination","value":"installation"},{"type":"Titre","value":"De Vermeer \u00e0 V\u00e9ron\u00e8se"}],"displayDateCreated":"Date de cr\u00e9ation\/fabrication : 2019","currentLocation":"non expos\u00e9","room":"","isMuseesNationauxRecuperation":false,"dateCreated":[{"startYear":"","endYear":2019,"imprecision":"","text":"Epoque contemporaine ; fin du XXe si\u00e8cle - d\u00e9but du XXIe si\u00e8cle","type":"Date de cr\u00e9ation\/fabrication","doubt":""}],"creator":[{"label":"Lain Rafael","attributionLevel":"Attribution actuelle","linkType":"","dates":[{"date":"1973","place":"Caxias do Sul","type":"date de naissance"}],"creatorRole":"","authenticationType":"","doubt":"","attributedBy":"","attributedYear":"","wikidata":""},{"label":"Detanico Angela","attributionLevel":"Attribution actuelle","linkType":"","dates":[{"date":"1974","place":"Caxias do Sul","type":"date de naissance"}],"creatorRole":"","authenticationType":"","doubt":"","attributedBy":"","attributedYear":"","wikidata":""}],"objectNumber":[{"value":"RFML.HL.2019.30.1","type":"Num\u00e9ro principal"}],"collection":"Service de l\u0027Histoire du Louvre","printsDrawingsEntity":"","printsDrawingsCollection":"","objectType":"","originalObject":"","printState":"","description":"Pour le nouveau b\u00e2timent du Centre de Conservation du Louvre, Angela Detanico et Rafael Lain ont con\u00e7u un portrait conceptuel de la collection du mus\u00e9e. Dans un grand cadre correspondant en taille au plus grand tableau du Louvre, \u0022Les Noces de Cana\u0022 de V\u00e9ron\u00e8se, ils ont assembl\u00e9 diff\u00e9rents formats de peintures issues de la collection, jusqu\u0027\u00e0 la toute petite \u0022Denteli\u00e8re\u0022 de Vermeer. Les dimensions de chaque tableau ont \u00e9t\u00e9 mat\u00e9rialis\u00e9es p